log
@ray(4) is no more
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: ray.4,v 1.26 2013/07/16 16:05:49 schwarze Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: ray.4,v 1.5 2000/02/28 13:54:55 enami Exp $
